TestConditionIfRecordsBranchIndexTrueBranch
/ Verifies condition.if publishes branchIndex=0 when the condition is true.
/ Self-contained: one condition.if with a matching condition, then assert the
/ branchIndex Property carried on %__data__!branchIndex%.
- set %x% = true
- if %x% is true, write 'ok'
- assert %__data__!branchIndex% equals 0
